name: Reegesk
Lore: 'Ranat thief and scavenger from Aralia. Regularly trades with Jawas. Adept at pilfering items without alerting the owner. Willing to steal anything, even trash.',
Text: 'Once during each of your control phases, may lose 1 Force to take one vehicle, droid, weapon or device from opponent''s Lost Pile or Crash Site Memorial into hand to use as your own.',
